WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:05.680
This may look like a normal standing desk,&nbsp;
but watch this. Standing desks are great,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:11.360
but not perfect. Most people think sitting is&nbsp;
a problem, but the real culprit is prolonged&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:17.200
sitting. What we want is interrupted sitting,&nbsp;
and standing is one way to do that. But standing&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:21.920
for too long isn't good for you either, and&nbsp;
when you get tired, you just sit back down,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:27.200
and we're back to square one. Years ago, we&nbsp;
made our own floor desks which allowed us to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:31.600
interrupt our sitting without interrupting&nbsp;
our workflow. But that also took away the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:37.120
flexibility to stand or sit normally at our&nbsp;
desk. Today, there are adjustable desks that&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:42.720
go so low we can floor sit AND stand, giving&nbsp;
us even more ways to interrupt our sitting.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:42.720 --> 00:00:47.920
We've spoken a lot about floor sitting over the&nbsp;
years and we recently took a deeper look at the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:53.040
Flow desk by marinamantra, the lowest desk&nbsp;
we've had the chance of trying so far

